DESCRIPTION:Request for parents to inform the school office if their child will not be returning to BWA in September.\n\nMiss Henry requests that parents inform the school office in writing as soon as possible if their child will not be returning to BWA in September. This assists with class organization and staffing for the next academic year. Please include details of the new school if known.
